cat << EOF
The Non Tool Kit (NTK) is a fork of the Fast Light ToolKit library,
adding improved graphics rendering via Cairo, a streamlined and
enhanced widget set, and other features designed to improve
the appearance and performance of the Non applications.
NTK is included in the Non distribution.
